name: Humangear GoBites Quattro
description: A complete personal utensil set at a very civilized weight and bulk. Elegant touches include a double ended toothpick and a pair of travel chopsticks. Everything fits into a thin, light case to stay clean and organized.Deep fork tines spear food or twirl noodles.Tapered splitter tines on sides cut food efficiently.Easy-scrape spoon profile gets the last mouthfuls.Long toothpick has a wedge at one end and a point at the other.Travel chopsticks give a variety of eating options.
